	<div class="entry-content">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Mission</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">To ensure excellent instruction, research and community extension for the overall development of Asiatechian<br>
committed in practicing professionalism and in meeting the demands of local, national and global communities</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Vision</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">By 2035, Asiatech is one of a premiere academic institution in the Country<br>
continuously developing highly competent, innovative and values-driven Asiatechian.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
</p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Core Values</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Accountable<br>
Service-Oriented<br>
Innovative<br>
Adaptive<br>
Team-oriented<br>
Efficient<br>
Committed<br>
Honest<br>
Industrious<br>
Articulate<br>
Noble</p>
